latestIgtvVideos.title: QUICK GREEN EYE LOOK

latestPosts.caption:
Still processing this moment 🥹♥️🧿✨

If I can do it, anyone can! Saying this because I know the girl I used to be the one who only dreamt of being on camera, without knowing how, when, or what would make it happen. And today, being awarded for it? Feels surreal.

This wouldn’t have been possible without my biggest support system my husband, my family, and my friends who kept watching my videos, cheering me on every step of the way.

Vivek, thank you for believing in me, for pushing me to chase what I truly wanted, and for making me realize I can fly higher than I ever imagined.

To my family, thank you for trusting me, for understanding how much this meant to me.

And to my amazing friends, who always said “Tu bas videos daal daily, hum dekhenge… aur subscribe bhi karwa denge sabse!” 😭🫶🏻

This win is as much yours as it is mine!

Bug big thanks to @youtubecreatorsindia @youtubeindia @youtube
